data.description: This 2 story duplex is perfect for investors and private residents alike. Located in the Coleman Park revitalization area, public transportation across the street and within walking distance of downtown, you're never too far from where you want to be. Each of the 2 units has 2 bd/1bath, separate water & electric meters, five total parking spots, and independent entrances to each unit. Both units feature updated flooring, newer appliances, and in-unit laundry. With a lot size of over 5400 sqr ft, this property boasts a spacious backyard. Yard is totally enclosed with concrete wall anf fencing for privacy and security. Exterior security camera system on premises, security cameras conveys. Monitoring service will be the responsibility of the buyer. No HOA fees.
